1
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,280
Nineteen minutes and thirty-five seconds.

2
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:00,840
It seems

3
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,850
my performance passed.

4
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:03,640
Of course.

5
00:01:04,440 --> 00:01:05,519
Truly worthy of being

6
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:07,680
the famous genius racer of the past,

7
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:09,520
He Nan.

8
00:01:13,880 --> 00:01:15,680
Why aren't you refuting, Mr. He?

9
00:01:16,440 --> 00:01:17,520
Did I guess right?

10
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,039
Boss Ye,

11
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,820
what are you joking about?

12
00:01:22,960 --> 00:01:25,280
I am Gu Haoran, the second young master of the Gu family.

13
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,680
The He Nan you mentioned,

14
00:01:26,880 --> 00:01:27,810
I don't know him.

15
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:29,920
No matter how capable Young Master Gu is,

16
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:32,380
he could never possess such driving skills.

17
00:01:32,759 --> 00:01:33,440
Unless

18
00:01:34,280 --> 00:01:35,680
he's a different person.

19
00:01:38,440 --> 00:01:39,160
Actually, I...

20
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:40,400
Are you trying to say,

21
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:42,400
actually, I had an expert's guidance,

22
00:01:42,400 --> 00:01:43,160
or

23
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,490
I've been hiding my true strength?

24
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:48,560
You don't even need to speak.

25
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,360
I know how you're going to argue.

26
00:01:51,800 --> 00:01:53,729
This Ye Lan really has some tricks.

27
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:56,140
How does she know my identity?

28
00:01:56,520 --> 00:01:57,520
Handsome boy,

29
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:59,280
are you that nervous?

30
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,600
It seems I was right.

31
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,200
I'm really not.

32
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:06,880
I am a know-it-all in the racing world.

33
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,720
Do you really think

34
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,199
your little tricks

35
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:11,880
can hide from my sharp eyes?

36
00:02:18,079 --> 00:02:19,079
Don't be nervous.

37
00:02:19,760 --> 00:02:22,090
I am not interested in your true identity.

38
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:24,410
Whether you are He Nan or Gu Haoran,

39
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:27,120
it won't affect me doing business with you.

40
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,000
Don't be nervous.

41
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:37,010
I am not interested in your true identity.

42
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:39,329
Whether you are He Nan or Gu Haoran,

43
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:42,000
it won't affect me doing business with you.

44
00:02:44,760 --> 00:02:46,400
Ye Lan has already gone this far.

45
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:48,720
I can't believe this Gu Haoran still won't admit it.

46
00:02:48,720 --> 00:02:50,560
I already have the answer.

47
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,620
Mr. Qianye,

48
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,040
who exactly is he?

49
00:02:54,440 --> 00:02:55,720
He is the

50
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,680
genius racer,

51
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:58,920
He Nan.

52
00:03:04,880 --> 00:03:05,880
Just as I thought.

53
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:08,520
This Gu Haoran is a fake.

54
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:12,520
No wonder his driving skills improved so fast.

55
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:13,840
Come on.

56
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,330
Have a drink with me.

57
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,020
No, thanks.

58
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:17,640
What?

59
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:19,530
Are you afraid I drugged it?

60
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:23,960
I'm afraid of being stopped for drunk driving on the way down.

61
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:25,440
Many people want to drink with me,

62
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,840
but never get the chance.

63
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,400
I've already given you the performance you wanted to see.

64
00:03:30,400 --> 00:03:32,730
Isn't it time you fulfilled your promise?

65
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,520
You really are a killjoy.

66
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:35,530
Fine.

67
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,480
I'll tell you.

68
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,680
Chen Zixi was investigating

69
00:03:38,680 --> 00:03:39,920
the deliberate smearing of

70
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,240
TG new energy vehicles.

71
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,640
That's why she was targeted.

72
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:43,240
After all,

73
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:46,480
cutting off someone's livelihood is like killing their parents.

74
00:03:46,480 --> 00:03:48,480
Whose interests did she infringe upon?

75
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:49,810
I don't know about that.

76
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:50,920
I can only say

77
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,720
that many big shots in the racing circle

78
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:55,579
don't want new energy vehicles to enter the market.

79
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,200
This will impact the interest chain

80
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,680
of traditional fuel vehicles.

81
00:03:58,680 --> 00:04:00,680
You might be able to start from here.

82
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:02,680
Thank you.

83
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:03,560
Wait.

84
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,450
What do you want?

85
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:09,560
I just want to know

86
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,960
where you got the news

87
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,960
that Chen Zixi came to see me.

88
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,200
Guess.

89
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:20,079
You can keep your secrets.

90
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:22,680
But if you want my help next time,

91
00:04:23,000 --> 00:04:25,000
don't play smart with me.

92
00:04:25,400 --> 00:04:27,130
The consequences of teasing me

93
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:28,920
are terrible.

94
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:34,520
What exactly is

95
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:36,640
this woman up to?

96
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:40,560
Ye Lan.

97
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,560
As expected, few men

98
00:04:42,640 --> 00:04:44,240
can resist your temptation.

99
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:47,450
You flatter me, Mr. Qianye.

100
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:51,080
That kid won't trust me easily.

101
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:53,760
We let that kid escape back then.

102
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:54,760
This time,

103
00:04:56,159 --> 00:04:58,090
we must kill him with our own hands.

104
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,980
Did I ever say I wanted to kill him?

105
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:01,700
Mr. Qianye,

106
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,160
I didn't mean that.

107
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:05,840
Such a genius racer

108
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,240
dying like this

109
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:09,040
would be a pity.

110
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,800
Instead,

111
00:05:11,760 --> 00:05:14,480
let's have some fun with him.

112
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:28,320
More than half of the racing world opposed the TG project back then.

113
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,580
Looking for clues here

114
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:31,730
is like finding a needle in a haystack.

115
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:36,420
Will we find any clues if we go to the Chen family?

116
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:41,080
Speak of the devil.

117
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:42,920
Gu Haoran.

118
00:05:43,360 --> 00:05:45,120
Come to my house

119
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,240
right now.

120
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,360
Ziqing,

121
00:05:47,640 --> 00:05:48,440
what's wrong?

122
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,560
I have no time for nonsense with you.

123
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:51,120
Hurry up.

124
00:05:52,520 --> 00:05:53,200
Okay, okay, okay.

125
00:05:53,200 --> 00:05:54,400
I'll leave right now.

126
00:05:54,960 --> 00:05:56,490
Did you swallow gunpowder?

127
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,120
Ziqing.

128
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,620
What's the emergency?

129
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,080
Gu Haoran.

130
00:06:14,120 --> 00:06:15,800
You must explain this to me clearly today.

131
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:16,930
What does this mean?

132
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:18,690
How do you have this?

133
00:06:19,400 --> 00:06:20,330
Did you stalk me?

134
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,720
How is that possible?

135
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:24,520
My friend saw it with his own eyes when he went drinking.

136
00:06:24,520 --> 00:06:26,240
That lady boss is an information broker.

137
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,880
I happened to have something to ask her.

138
00:06:27,880 --> 00:06:29,720
You could have come to me if you needed something.

139
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,980
If I couldn't help you,

140
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:32,880
I could have asked my friends to look into it for you.

141
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:34,280
It wasn't anything important.

142
00:06:34,280 --> 00:06:35,540
No need to trouble you.

143
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,480
Then why couldn't you ask someone else?

144
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:39,409
Why did it have to be that lady boss?

145
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,480
Ziqing.

146
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,800
I admit I shouldn't have met

147
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:05,930
another girl alone.

148
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:06,850
I apologize.

149
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:08,320
I'm sorry.

150
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,400
All right.

151
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:15,320
I'll forgive you for now.

152
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,040
But

153
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,680
you have to promise me one thing.

154
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:20,480
What is it?

155
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:21,890
Drink with me

156
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:24,440
until I'm drunk.

157
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,320
Drink.

158
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:27,640
Sure.

159
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:30,930
Let's go.

160
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,120
Haoran.

161
00:07:36,720 --> 00:07:37,480
Teach me

162
00:07:37,960 --> 00:07:40,280
how to drive a car from one building

163
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,159
to another.

164
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,000
Ziqing.

165
00:07:45,640 --> 00:07:46,840
You've had too much to drink.

166
00:07:46,840 --> 00:07:49,040
Let me help you back to your room to rest.

167
00:08:13,280 --> 00:08:14,360
Don't go.

168
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:24,500
It's not Zixi's phone number.

169
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:26,100
And it's not her birthday.

170
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,180
Then what else could it be?

171
00:09:29,800 --> 00:09:30,800
It's my birthday.

172
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,320
It worked.

173
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:09,880
Shiqi.

174
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:12,300
I found the file Zixi left.

175
00:10:12,840 --> 00:10:14,280
Please help me decrypt it.

176
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:15,140
Okay, Captain.

177
00:10:16,280 --> 00:10:17,740
I'll bring it to you later.

178
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:19,100
No problem.

179
00:10:53,240 --> 00:10:53,840
Gu Haoran.

180
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:57,360
Ziqing.
